videos.description: Taylor Robertson hits a big 3 for Oklahoma off an inbounds play as Oklahoma leads No. 1 UConn in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Robertson drains big 3 for Oklahoma

videos.headline: Robertson drains 3 from corner for Sooners
